name: FSM-parse-dom
description: 1. Access-Control-Allow-Origin 设置哪个源可以访问我   2. Access-Control-Allow-Headers 允许携带哪个头访问我   3. Access-Control-Allow-Methods 允许哪个方法访问我   4. Access-Control-Allow-Credentials 允许携带 cookie   5. Access-Control-Max-Age 预检的存活时间   6. Access-Control-Expose-Headers 允许返回的头，把响应头暴露出去给前端
